jumping out of her chair,
"Archery, archery!"

465
00:22:47,166 --> 00:22:49,066
And it was pretty late
that we were giving her

466
00:22:49,435 --> 00:22:51,925
the choice of which event
that she could compete in.

467
00:22:52,371 --> 00:22:55,121
But I think it really solidified it
that she now has...

468
00:22:56,041 --> 00:22:56,890
She's in a power position.

