00:23:00,913 --> 00:23:02,493
here are the rules of this thing,

471
00:23:02,815 --> 00:23:05,035
that it is customary for a princess

472
00:23:05,451 --> 00:23:08,851
to pick the competition
for these guys to compete in.

473
00:23:09,421 --> 00:23:13,291
It just kind of lines up
how she's going to solve this problem.

474
00:23:13,926 --> 00:23:15,916
‘Cause she has no way out. Right?

475
00:23:16,295 --> 00:23:18,755
She's stuck in this. How possibly
is she gonna get out of this?

476
00:23:19,198 --> 00:23:20,928
We wanted to feel like
she was backed into a corner.

477
00:23:21,267 --> 00:23:23,457
So you would forgive her for
going against her mom

478
00:23:23,869 --> 00:23:26,418
and trying to solve her own problem.

