00:25:28,961 --> 00:25:31,041
and causes this blowup
that turns into a fistfight.

520
00:25:31,430 --> 00:25:34,060
So as we worked on the story
we kind of dialed in

521
00:25:34,533 --> 00:25:36,233
and made it these
very specific characters

