00:25:36,568 --> 00:25:40,258
that she's showing up
instead of the kind of general crowd.

523
00:25:40,873 --> 00:25:42,363
Right. Which works really well because

524
00:25:42,674 --> 00:25:45,954
we establish in the scene before
that this is part of the tradition.

525
00:25:46,512 --> 00:25:47,881
This is a thing that happens

526
00:25:48,180 --> 00:25:51,990
and that there are
specific rules for this tradition.

