00:26:07,599 --> 00:26:11,668
and made everybody look like fools
and that's what leads to this big blowup.

532
00:26:13,372 --> 00:26:15,072
But we're wanting to
agree with her at this point.

533
00:26:15,407 --> 00:26:17,867
-We are forcing her into a corner.
-Yeah, we're one on her side.

534
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:20,040
I mean, what princess would want to be

535
00:26:20,379 --> 00:26:22,658
forced to marry somebody
she doesn't want to?

536
00:26:23,082 --> 00:26:25,192
The idea of the dress ripping
has been there forever.

537
00:26:25,584 --> 00:26:28,454
Because it's, again,
another symbol of Mom

538
00:26:28,954 --> 00:26:31,384
and the way Mom has identified Merida.

539
00:26:31,824 --> 00:26:35,224
And Merida is pushing back against
that in a really visual, tangible way.

540
00:26:36,562 --> 00:26:39,022
And for a long time she was never able
to make the third shot.

541
00:26:39,465 --> 00:26:41,635
Mom was always able
to stop that third shot.

542
00:26:42,067 --> 00:26:44,937
And then Nick here says,
"What if she does win?"

