00:33:11,156 --> 00:33:13,816
And he would mutter to himself,
"lL was a man. l was a man."

679
00:33:14,292 --> 00:33:15,581
We thought that was fantastic.

680
00:33:15,861 --> 00:33:18,881
And so Steve actually
does the voice of the Crow.

681
00:33:19,397 --> 00:33:21,706
And he does an excellent job.

682
00:33:22,133 --> 00:33:24,593
We knew in the sequence
it was a pivotal moment

683
00:33:25,036 --> 00:33:28,936
for Merida to get the device
that was going to alter her life

