00:59:31,835 --> 00:59:35,345
And then the Witch is
one of the hubs of this story.

1266
00:59:35,939 --> 00:59:37,489
And that the wisps
are leading them here

1267
00:59:37,808 --> 00:59:40,358
so that Merida can find those answers.

1268
00:59:40,811 --> 00:59:45,281
And I wanted it to be a very stark place,
just devoid of life and color.

1269
00:59:45,282 --> 00:59:45,922
And I wanted it to be a very stark place,
just devoid of life and color.

1270
00:59:46,116 --> 00:59:47,426
And that's an actual broch.

1271
00:59:47,717 --> 00:59:49,467
That's what they look like in Scotland.

