01:00:22,719 --> 01:00:25,939
and her hair, even though it's red,
it's very pale.

1283
01:00:27,290 --> 01:00:28,870
It's like an illustrated book.

1284
01:00:29,192 --> 01:00:34,412
Yeah. But seeing this location
colorless, gray, dead.

