1286
01:00:38,869 --> 01:00:40,569
Exactly. And we're tying it all together.

1287
01:00:40,904 --> 01:00:43,454
And that's why the wisps
ultimately lead her here.

1288
01:00:43,907 --> 01:00:46,837
So she can put together
and solve this mystery.

