of Brenda's story that

1775
01:25:05,834 --> 01:25:08,023
the resolution is a love story
between a mother and daughter.

1776
01:25:08,437 --> 01:25:11,687
And I don't know that
we've seen a lot of that in movies.

1777
01:25:12,240 --> 01:25:13,110
-Yeah.
-Especially family movies.

1778
01:25:13,342 --> 01:25:14,192
Well, you bookend that

1779
01:25:14,409 --> 01:25:17,509
Merida was having her favorite day
with Angus at the beginning of the film.

1780
01:25:18,046 --> 01:25:20,626
And now Mom has joined her
in her world,

1781
01:25:21,083 --> 01:25:23,893
I think wraps their characters up
quite nicely.

1782
