01:26:13,035 --> 01:26:15,644
But that you have that resolution
of their characters,

1801
01:26:16,104 --> 01:26:18,714
and in the song,
the song's words are basically saying,

1802
01:26:19,174 --> 01:26:22,274
"We are what we are, and that's okay."

1803
01:26:22,811 --> 01:26:26,590
Getting to see them riding together,
even without that archery moment,

1804
01:26:27,215 --> 01:26:28,235
you sort of feel like...

1805
01:26:28,483 --> 01:26:30,263
I think we all believe that Mom

1806
01:26:30,619 --> 01:26:32,579
was quite a bit like Merida
when she was young.

